    <intervention_type>Behavioral</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Symptom Education</intervention_name>
    <description>Participants are given a Symptom Education Toolkit at baseline and at each visit thereafter (1 month and 3 month) are encouraged to use the Toolkit for symptoms they are experiencing. They are also encouraged to use resources available to them.</description>
